(21, 21, 'projects_category', 'Building a construction in an active hospital environment is perhaps the most complex and challenging work in the industry. Maintaining safety, keeping a low level of noise and collaborating with facility''s staff requires an extremely well planned management. These are the keys to successfully completing the work with no interruption of services and minimal inconvenience to the patients, residents and staff members.\r\nWe''ve got all the experience that''s needed to perform both a new construction and a renovation in a continuously inhabited and operating environment. Builderra has constructed more than 800 significant healthcare facilities and renovated thousands more. Our company''s name consistently pops on Modern Healthcare''s Top five list of leading healthcare construction management companies. Rest assured that our credentials, experience and in-house expertise benefit every healthcare construction project we undertake!', 0, 5),
(22, 22, 'projects_category', 'Educational institutions can be much more creative, than your regular school or a college campus!\r\nOur bright team of designers and architects will easily sketch a fresh-looking look for your educational building in no time!\r\nDon''t underestimate the way the building looks, as it will be one of the first things that your prospective students will look at when deciding whether to enroll or not!\r\nEntrust us with building your campuses or studying facilities and the result will be mesmerizing!', 0, 5),
(23, 23, 'projects_category', 'It''s probably the most diverse category of construction to work in. But we''ve got experience of building both small shopping malls and 50-stories high-rises!\r\nWe''re confident that a deliberate management system, on par with efficient designing can make any architectural dream come true...\r\nOur level of expertise allows us to build  approach commercial structures of different sizes with the same kind of efficiency...\r\nThe fact that we''ve built 12 business towers and dozens of smaller facilities tells about our integrity and adaptability!', 0, 5),
(24, 24, 'projects_category', 'Building a manufacturing facility or a factory house can be much more challenging, than building a cottage house. Entrust us in such a complex task!\r\nBuilderry construction company has been building new manufacturing and industrial facilities, as well as renovating existing facilities all over the US for many years...\r\nOur specialties of expertise included projects that had very strict scheduling, required elaborate design/build projecting, and also projects where on-going operations must not have been interrupted by construction activities.\r\nWe''ve done hundreds of complex projects on “fast track” schedule.', 0, 5),
(25, 25, 'projects_category', 'While doing a head quarters building for an IT company is relatively easy, we''ve also got our hands at constructing more challenging types of IT related structures...\r\nFew data centers that we''ve built for such IT giants as Google, Yelp, Microsoft and AOL can serve as an example of our expertise in the field.\r\nBut the cherry on the pie of our expertise in that field is actually the Yahoo''s project...\r\nThat construction took us good 4 years to get built, but it paid off immensely, as Yahoo managed to expand its initially planned usage 4 fold!', 0, 5),
(26, 26, 'projects_category', 'The US military and States governments used our expertise and manpower to build numerous military-grade, cost-efficient and usage-practical buildings, all over the US, as well as overseas...\r\nOur experience in being government contractors also includes works on infrastructure and superstructure projects, such as highways. bridges and miscellaneous government office buildings...', 0, 5),
(27, 27, 'projects_category', 'Working on a socially important building, such as a park involves additional landscape construction expertise. Thankfully, we''ve got it and we aren''t afraid to apply it in practice!\r\nOverall, we''ve managed to build many hotels, resorts and casinos! It''s important to note that constructing the entertainment type of buildings is not so much of a fun, but rather a lot of hard work that we''re willing to do!', 0, 5),
(28, 28, 'projects_category', 'While building a warehouse for an e-store is no easy feat itself, think about building it for Amazon or Google! We''ve already done that, so no complexity can scare us off the project!\r\nIn fact, as we were working on completing this 500, 000 sq. ft sized warehouse, we''ve excelled our time management and contractors supervision skills upwards!', 0, 5),
